{"tid":2405663,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被問會否停播BBC節目 無綫暫不置評 有線沒有回應","createTime":"2021-02-12T14:10:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-13T04:04:38.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"02a3884b73acc87364fc4fe6cbaf9e1e1aee106c","tid":2405663,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T14:10:53.000Z","msg":"被問會否停播BBC節目 無綫暫不置評 有線沒有回應<br />\n<br />\n國家廣播電視總局通報，不允許英國廣播公司BBC世界新聞台繼續在中國境內落地，不受理新一年度落地申請，認為BBC涉華的報道內容，違反新聞應當真實、公正的要求。<br />\n<br />\n本港的三間電視台有收費頻道24小時轉播BBC節目，記者查詢會否跟隨國家廣電總局通報停播相關節目，其中無綫對外事務科表示，正觀察情况和發展，也有合約期限的考慮，暫不予置評； 有線電視外事部稱沒有回應。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575476-20210212.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575476-20210212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FPUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=14bfb9a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1575476-20210212.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=676070bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1575476-20210212.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"216c8c76462c8e53fd1871dd655ef3096f24b4a3","tid":2405663,"uid":100581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T16:05:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">快Ｄ停晒佢啦！</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"50a94127bb1b6232c235583a2fecea593c86912b","tid":2405663,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T16:20:43.000Z","msg":"仲唔跟国家做嘢？"},{"pid":"f63c21e1c88425d28e8d2cd1430b0cafad847116","tid":2405663,"uid":325346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T16:45:25.000Z","msg":"無得睇BBC節目會係香港人的損失"},{"pid":"6c5eccf3aafd72c54b23fbd0dbb32caa0cf72923","tid":2405663,"uid":41243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T03:23:38.000Z","msg":"以前支那賤狗發癲bam呢樣